title: Woman who fired gun at Michigan Home Depot shoplifters enters plea
text:
Published By: Fox News - Today 
A customer who shot at shoplifters fleeing a Detroit-area Home Depot parking lot has pleaded no contest to reckless discharge of a firearm....
